title: Should the number of seats on the Spartan Council be increased to 8?
body:
[SCCP-66](https://sips.synthetix.io/SCCP/sccp-66) proposes to configure the Spartan Council seat members defined in [SIP-93](https://sips.synthetix.io/sips/sip-93) from 7 to 8.

Are you in favor of this decision?
author: 0xbeBF7295A9Ddc37e33609790b12FBe3dAF93cC73
